<p><strong><a href="/wanderers:behemoth-ants">巨兽与蚂蚁</a></strong><br />
<span style="color:grey"><span style="font-size:1em"><strong><tt>[+15](+19/-4)</tt></strong> <strong><tt>8</tt></strong><span style="font-size:0.9em;">评论 / 最近评论 <tt><strong>NoSeeSay</strong></tt> <tt><strong><span class="odate time_1556428619 format_%25y-%25m-%25d%20%25H%3A%25M">28 Apr 2019 05:16</span></strong></tt> 最近编辑 <tt><strong>Kirov-GT</strong></tt> <tt><strong><span class="odate time_1556349530 format_%25y-%25m-%25d%20%25H%3A%25M">27 Apr 2019 07:18</span></strong></tt></span></span></span></p>

    
    
    
